snippet: The straw poll, conducted at the annual Conservative Political Action Conference, reflects the enthusiastic reception that Mr. Paul, a libertarian senator, received at the event.
abstract: Sen Rand Paul, Republican of Kentucky, wins presidential straw poll at prominent conservative conference, capturing 31 percent of the vote among no fewer than 10 potential candidates.
lead_paragraph: The straw poll, conducted at the annual Conservative Political Action Conference, reflects the enthusiastic reception that Mr. Paul, a libertarian senator, received at the event.

headline.main: Rand Paul Wins Conservative Straw Poll
